dct_title_s: Map of the country between Leh and Ilchí showing the routes taken by Mr. Johnson, Civil Assist. G.T. Survey in 1865 / [engraved by] Edwd. Weller
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Boundary of Kashmir and Mr. Johnson's route are shown. Ilchí Province contemporary name is Hotan Xian.
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1867.
